Subject: Wisdom Caution Attention Source

Description: Raw preserved source for promoting wisdom and caution from scattered signals into an attention pattern.

& [DictatedWisdomCautionAttentionSource] is the preserved user source for wisdom and caution attention
  @ [user_statement] "where are Wisdom and Caution? was that part of the Attention.sop file exclusively?"
  @ [user_statement] "I was wondering if they should be promoted to their own attention pattern."

  + [observed_state] is Caution existed as a scattered signal in attention impressions, critique, fault, boundary, and proof contexts
  + [observed_gap] is Wisdom was not yet a live first-layer attention pattern in F:\.sop
  + [promotion_candidate] is Wisdom and Caution should become a paired attention governor
  + [wisdom] is the integrative governor that decides what may be accepted, folded, held, or realized
  + [caution] is the boundary governor that decides what must be tested, narrowed, deferred, rejected, or preserved outside
  + [paired_pattern_reason] is wisdom and caution are cleanest when they gate the same candidate from complementary sides

  = must: keep wisdom distinct from novelty pull or pleasing coherence
  = must: keep caution distinct from fear, refusal, or thought-stopping
  = must: use the pattern before promoting traversal output into durable realization
  - never: treat intuition, heat, or correlation as proof without support and boundary checks
